Affiliate,Spice,is,a,technology,that,helps,affiliates,monetize,online,content,The,Affiliate,Spice,toolkit,provides,tools,for,creating,content,units,across,multiple,affiliate,networks,and,tools,for,automatically,converting,links,into,affiliate,links,The,technology,is,available,as,JavaScript,widgets,and,as,a,RESTful,API,The,Affiliate,Spice,API,allows,developers,to,use,the,technology,in,their,own,applications,such,as,in,web,apps,mobile,apps,Android,apps,iPhone,apps,and,iPad,apps,Affiliates,can,quickly,build,links,inside,their,own,application,or,website,to,thousands,of,advertisers,and,millions,of,products,via,the,API